\c 17
\s Vanhu havamunzwisisi, saka Jobho
\s anokumbira kuti Mwari
\s amururamisire
\v 1 Mweya wangu wapera, mazuva angu adzima,
\s Hwiro hunondimirira.
\p
\v 2 Zvirokwazvo, vanondiseka vaneni; Ziso rangu rinoramba richiona kutsamwa kwavo.
\p
\v 3 Zvino ndipikirei, muve rubatso rwangu kwamuri;
\s Ndianiko achabatana maoko neni?
\p
\v 4 Nokuti makavanzira mwoyo yavo kunzwisisa;
\s Naizvozvo hamungavakudzi.
\p
\v 5 Iye, anokwirira shamwari dzake kuti dzitapwe,
\s Meso avana vake achapera.
\p
\v 6 Iye akandiita shumo pakati
\s pavanhu;
\s Ndinosemwa pachena.
\p
\v 7 Ziso rangu harichaoni nemhaka yokuchema,
\s Mitezo yangu yose yafanana
\s nomumwd.
\p
\v 8 Vanhu vakarurama vachakanuka nazvo,
\s Asine mhaka achamukira vasingadi Mwari.
\p
\v 9 Kunyange zvakadaro akarurama
\s acharambira panzira yake,
\s Uye ana maoko akanaka
\s acharamba achisimba.
\p
\v 1 Â° Asi imi mose dzokai, muuye zvino;
\s Nokuti handingawani munhu
\s akangwara pakati penyu. "Mazuva angu apfuura,
\s zvandaivavarira zvakona,
\s Iyo mifungo yomwoyo wangu.
\p
\v 12 Vanoshandura usiku ave masikati; Vanoti, "Chiedza chiri pedyo nerima."
\p
\v 13 Kana ndine tariro, Sheori ndiyo imba yangu;
\s Ndakawadza nhovo yangu murima;
\p
\v 14 Ndakati kuhwiro, "Ndiwe baba vangu;"
\s Nokuhonye, "Ndiwe mai vangu nehanzvadzi yangu;"
\p
\v 15 Zvino tariro yangu iripiko?
\s Kana iri tariro yangu, ndianiko angaiona?
\p
\v 16 Ichaburukira kumazariro eSheori,
\s Kana zororo yavapo paguruva.
